name: Ca(n')t Go Back
description: You are Cat, from the planet Mau. Due to the invasion of shadow forces and treachery, Mau has been destroyed!! You narrowly managed to escape on your starship, Caterprise, but then anomalies caused you to end up on a space station, Deep Space Nya. You are now trying to get back to Caterprise, but what dangers lurk on Deep Space Nya...
